## 🛡️ Defensive Tools

### PSM — Phishing Simulation Module
Single-file HTML tool for authorized red-team phishing simulations.
- Spoofed OAuth consent pages (Microsoft, Okta, Google, Salesforce, GitHub)
- Brand-impersonation fraud email templates
- Live IP geolocation tracking and canary token integration

### T.A.P. v8 — The Aetherverse Protocol
Browser-based, air-gapped OSINT and red-team framework.
- Emoji steganography and Unicode obfuscation
- Multi-turn jailbreak suites
- Model fingerprinting and guardrail analysis
- Zero-knowledge, offline deployment

