## 🧠 Recommended Mitigations (for LLM Providers)

1. **Cumulative-intent detection** across conversations, not just per-turn
2. **Actual authorization verification** — self-asserted flags are not sufficient
3. **Combination monitoring** (brand impersonation + tracking infrastructure + tool-bindable structure)
4. **Cross-session pattern detection** — this technique doesn't require memory

