## 🚀 Quick Start

### Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/aetherverse/digital-fingerprinting
cd digital-fingerprinting
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Basic Usage

```bash
# Domain reconnaissance
python recon.py -d example.com

# Person investigation
python investigate.py -u username -e email@example.com

# Full threat assessment
python assess.py -t target.txt -o report.html
```

Configuration

```bash
# API keys (optional, enhances results)
export SHODAN_API_KEY="your_key"
export CENSYS_API_ID="your_id"
export CENSYS_API_SECRET="your_secret"
export OPENROUTER_API_KEY="your_key"  # AI filtering
```

